author: @Pamela._
content:
Madonna did not "gave us" anything. She ws really well paid by the largest brazilian bank + Heineken.
Those billboard that he saw were not from the people, but from all companies involved.
I think it's important to explain those things.
But yes, it was a really magnificent concert. We brazilians of all ages love Madonna!
